{"tid":285572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方東網集團-  「鴉片面膜」易上癮　含類固醇致過敏","createTime":"2017-06-16T02:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T11:27:14.000Z","uid":3117,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"caef387355b41288a152ddbcd7d5cabf5c416086","tid":285572,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"不法商人被揭發在面膜添加被指是「皮膚鴉片」的化妝品禁用物質糖皮質激素。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=BAGSEZDZK7E%2BO3%2BVeop%2F%2B0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=99caf6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】網購「鴉片面膜」，小心隨時上癮！有內地傳媒報道，不法商人為了加速片裝面膜的神奇功效，在面膜添加被指是「皮膚鴉片」的化妝品禁用物質糖皮質激素。廣東省食品藥品監督管理局日前抽查當地逾130款網購面膜，發現逾2成4含禁用的糖皮質激素。香港醫學界人士警告，糖皮質激素為類固醇一種，藥性依賴性強，長期使用會導致上癮，一旦停用容易引致過敏症狀。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20160726/20160726050036lc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20160726%2F20160726050036lc.html&d=BAGSEZDZK7E%2BO3%2BVeop%2F%2B0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9a1fdfdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20160726/20160726050036lc.html</a>"},{"pid":"542675c34e70b78f2385c403cb58d8b65c9fb674","tid":285572,"uid":18638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:01:20.000Z","msg":"賣鴉片正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456197f55c360d7e1f7603c4f897653f5e7a9000","tid":285572,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71de9aac35c3d771d25f46d5b90fe5b6a17e4500","tid":285572,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"有無700噸？"},{"pid":"d51be619f7c96bfa7c0becc70b17444fc9bc0cdf","tid":285572,"uid":30807,"like":0,"di